main event: A UFO sighting involving two ball-shaped white objects with blue undersides was reported at FE Warren AFB, Wyoming on August 21, 1965.
interesting points: The objects were observed moving to the North at an estimated altitude of 5,000 feet,The sighting involved 5 confirmed military witnesses,Reports from the area during that month attributed sightings to astronautical objects,The conclusion of the report mentioned insufficient data for evaluation,No photographs or physical evidence were included in the report.
sighted object: two ball-shaped white objects with blue undersides
witness description: military personnel on duty at the airbase
